`useMemo` will only re-run the `expensiveCalculation` function if any of the values in its dependency array `[propA, propB]` change. If `propC` changes, but `propA` and `propB` remain the same, `MyComponent` will re-render, but `expensiveCalculation` will not execute again. If no dependencies change, `useMemo` returns the previously memoized value.

