In React Router v5:
```jsx
import { Redirect } from 'react-router-dom';
// ... in a class component render method
if (loggedIn) {
  return <Redirect to="/dashboard" />;
}
```
In React Router v6:
```jsx
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';
// ... in a functional component
const navigate = useNavigate();
// ... inside an event handler or useEffect
if (loggedIn) {
  navigate('/dashboard');
}
```
This example clarifies how `Redirect` (v5) is a component that you render, while `useNavigate` (v6) provides a function that you call.

